OL,3,CCharities and health experts warn
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts could cost lives
OL,6,FCharities and health experts have
OL,7,Fwarned welfare cuts could risk lives,
OL,8,Fas the Government prepared to publish
OL,9,Fan official impact assessment into how
OL,10,Fmany people will be affected by its
OL,11,Fplans.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,14,Fdescribed the current welfare system
OL,15,Fas "morally indefensible", insisting
OL,16,FLabour's reforms will help those who
OL,17,Fcan work to get jobs.
