OL,3,CCharities and health experts warn
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts could cost lives
OL,6,FBut the plans, announced last week, to
OL,7,Fcut #5 billion off the welfare bill
OL,8,Fhave been met with criticism from
OL,9,Fcharities as well as some of his own
OL,10,FMPs.
OL,12,FParty veteran Diane Abbott said there
OL,13,Fwas "nothing moral" about the plan and
OL,14,Faccused the Treasury of wishing to
OL,15,F"balance the country's books on the
OL,16,Fback of the most vulnerable and poor
OL,17,Fpeople in this society".
