OL,3,CCharities and health experts warn
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts could cost lives
OL,6,FMental health charity Mind said its
OL,7,Fhelpline advisers had reported that
OL,8,Fsome people had indicated their level
OL,9,Fof worry was such that they felt they
OL,10,Fhad "no choice but to end their own
OL,11,Flife".
OL,13,FThe charity's welfare advice line saw
OL,14,Fcalls rise from 90 the previous week
OL,15,Fto 182 last week, while other
OL,16,Finformation and support lines received
OL,17,Fmore than 2,540 calls, which was a 10%
OL,18,Frise on the previous week.
