OL,6,FDisability charity Scope said calls to
OL,7,Fits helpline on the day of the
OL,8,Fannouncement had more than doubled to
OL,9,F344 from 118 the week earlier, while
OL,10,Fits online community saw 20,000
OL,11,Finteractions on the day compared to
OL,12,F15,000 seven days before.
OL,14,FCitizens Advice saw views of its Pip
OL,15,Fadvice pages rise to almost 80,000
OL,16,Fviews last week, which was a 44% rise
OL,17,Ffrom the week before.
OL,19,FScope said people feel "abandoned by
OL,20,Fthe Government".
