OL,3,CCharities and health experts warn
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts could cost lives
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a group of public health
OL,7,Fexperts said further cuts to social
OL,8,Fsecurity could lead to deaths.
OL,10,FWriting in the British Medical Journal
OL,11,F(BMJ), they said the reforms, coming
OL,12,Fafter years of austerity, would have a
OL,13,Fdetrimental effect on already-
OL,14,Fvulnerable people.
