OL,3,CCharities and health experts warn
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts could cost lives
OL,6,FOne of the group, Professor Gerry
OL,7,FMcCartney ` a specialist in wellbeing
OL,8,Feconomy at the University of Glasgow,
OL,9,Fsaid: "There is now substantial
OL,10,Fevidence that cuts to social security
OL,11,Fsince 2010 have fundamentally harmed
OL,12,Fthe health of the UK population.
OL,14,F"Implementing yet more cuts will
OL,15,Ftherefore result in more premature
OL,16,Fdeaths. It is vital that the UK
OL,17,FGovernment understands this evidence
OL,18,Fand takes a different policy approach."
